      "text": "Greenlight is a real time collaboration workspace application. A room in Greenlight is a large two-dimensional space where users can create many collaborative apps, notes, images and web pages and manipulate them. [https://github.com/croquet/greenlight-core github], [https://tinlizzie.org/~ohshima/greenlight/?q=wa9ben5kwm tinlizzie]"
